Nkashwererwa Bukuru

Ibanyi arazire, oraamureebe angambire
Nkaba naabaire ekitebyo, yaija yangamba obugyenyi
Ntyo naamutega emikono, yaanyiha atyo omu g‘abasheki

Ibanyi abuzire, oraamureebe arangise
Okunshwera akaba atenzire, akaba annugiire bukuru 
Naamworeka empiiha omu ngaro, atyo yangamba obugyenyi

Ibanyi agyenzire, oraamucwe eriisho atahunama
Akaba atombekire, nikyo naamutwareire omu karugu kangye
Ku yaahikiremu okumwenya kwakoma, nikyo kirugiriireho okubura

Ibanyi anyangire, yaatwara n‘empiiha zangye 
Naaziha abaishiki bato, ngu nyowe ngizire entanana
Akitsyamuka andya amaisho, atandika kunjuma enkanyanya

Ibanyi angungire, orwabya orwangye akarunuga
Hati naarya ahu arikusiiba, nkihiirwa andeetera omwiguto 
Akaba atari muvumbi, baitu hati ngu naateera omurengye

Ibanyi ampungire, n‘abaana be akabeehuzya
Batuura bagahangire eirembo, ngu akaareetana baguubwa gye 
N‘obw‘omubiri gwangye gutakitagata, baitu ah‘abw‘abaana akaizire

Ibanyi angambwire, ngu akashobya okushwera orikumukira
Naabeiha ngu nimmutwariza nk‘omwana, kwonka nyowe mmutiina 
Obutoosha mmutsimbira amaju, na ku agamba timmugarurira

Ibanyi antuzire ki, eki ntamukoreire niki?
Oraamureebe amugambire ataahe, nyowe n‘abaana emitima etuhanami 
Eby‘abakuru ninza kwehangaana, abato abarugyemu aije ashangye abe

Ibanyi arazire, eshi okushwererwa bukuru n‘eihano
Ku oba waashwereirwe bukuru, okashwerwa orwingano rwawe! 
Hati ngarukire naahinduka enkuru, haakiri kuri ntarashweirwe

